  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; line-height: 1.8em; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><a href=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201506/db148ac8-51e1-49bc-974b-0b3231bb25cf.jpg\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201506/db148ac8-51e1-49bc-974b-0b3231bb25cf.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; height: 394px; border-right-width: 0px; width: 600px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tA good sign<br />\n\tA good sign may indicate something great will come along the way. What is the good sign? What can it possibly indicate?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They saw a good sign... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) waking up to a bright, sunny day<br />\n\t2) received a long-awaited call<br />\n\t3) winning a prize<br />\n\t4) great health check-up results<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t&ldquo;Come in,&rdquo; a voice was heard answering after Wolfe lightly knocked on the door. Holding onto his <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/folder\" target=\"_blank\">folder</a>, Wolfe took a deep breath as he entered the editor's office. The owner of the room looked up and smiled. That's a good sign, Wolfe thought. &ldquo;Good morning, editor. You would like to see me?&rdquo; Wolfe greeted. &ldquo;Yes, please have a seat,&rdquo; the editor replied. &ldquo;How are the articles coming along?&rdquo; the editor asked. Here it goes, Wolfe pushed out a smile and replied, &ldquo;They are still being worked on, but everything is going smoothly.&rdquo; The editor nodded <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/approvingly\" target=\"_blank\">approvingly</a>.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/163787461394/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p740303/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p740303\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742666/\">宁泽涛夺冠！ 怎样用四国英语夸他帅</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742058/\">你的思想 才是世界的主宰</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742747/\">为什么分手后妹子更心痛</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742745/\">五部原汁原味的纯英剧：带你从荧幕上走近英国</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742698/\">朝鲜自创时区 8月起时区推后30分钟</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p161331/\">新概念英语第一册Lesson 1  Excuse me</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742400/\">牛人英语学习的五个阶段</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742506/\">霸道总裁猫征服社交网：八字胡萌杀</a></li><li st