  "description": "<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/fanli/201309/39bb1175-c873-4a70-a84c-1750265340ac.jpg\" style=\"height: 223px; width: 221px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p740416\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tAlthough reggae music officially comes out of Jamaica, some of the most <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/durable\" target=\"_blank\">durable</a> exponents of this musical form emerge from Birmingham. &quot;Red Red Wine&quot;, a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/version\" target=\"_blank\">version</a> of a Neil Diamond song by UB40, which was in UK and US Number One Hit for them in the 1980s, spending 100 weeks in the British Charts. The band was formed by a group of friends in Birmingham in 1978. And 35 years on, UB40 are releasing their 20th studio album, which combines their reggae song with influences from country music. The title track from the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/album\" target=\"_blank\">album</a> Getting Over the Storm by UB40. When band members Brian Travers and Jimmy Brown came to the studio, I suggested that the title might be taken to refer to a recent <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/reshuffle\" target=\"_blank\">reshuffle</a>, which singer Ali Campbell left the group, and was replaced by his brother Duncan, to the fact that several of the band were recently declared <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bankrupt\" target=\"_blank\">bankrupt</a>, or to the current political situation in Britain.</p>\n<p>\n\tWell it's definitely not political, cause we're not over the storm as far as politics is concerned. So I mean to be honest, it was a track that we loved. And it only became the title to the album really at the last minute, but it can of course be <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/interprete\" target=\"_blank\">interpreted</a> in lots of ways. I think to some degree we've been through a storm.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(128,128,128); line-height: 25px;\">声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a class=\"creatLinks\" href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/tag/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: verdana, arial; border-bottom: rgb(0,90,148) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,90,148); line-height: 25px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"更多英语内容\">英语</a><span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(128,128,128); line-height: 25px;\">&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p740416/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p740416\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742666/\">宁泽涛夺冠！ 怎样用四国英语夸他帅</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742058/\">你的思想 才是世界的主宰</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742747/\">为什么分手后妹子更心痛</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742745/\">五部原汁原味的纯英剧：带你从荧幕上走近英国</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742698/\">朝鲜自创时区 8月起时区推后30分钟</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p161331/\">新概念英语第一册Lesson 1  Excuse me</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742400/\">牛人英语学习的五个阶段</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742506/\">霸道总裁猫征服社交网：八字胡萌杀</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px